title: Bug Martini (Web Comic) - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"BUG MARTINI" Web Comic

"Bug Martini" (bugmartini.com) by Adam Huber -- formerly just "Bug" or "Bug Comic" -- is a gag-a-day humorous Web comic.  It features caricatures of cockroaches as its characters, and pokes fun at a wide array of subjects with little pattern as to what will be lampooned.  The comics themselves rarely have a set punchline, often instead having a joke in each panel.

This torrent collects "Bug Martini" comics from the strip's debut in 2009 through the end of 2014.  The comics are compiled into a set of CBR files, one for each year.  Each comic's page includes its title
